# Promotion Model

Instead of changing code:

```text
Feature Branch
      ↓
PR Review
      ↓
QA Apply
      ↓
Integration Testing
      ↓
Promote same module version
      ↓
PreProd
      ↓
CAB Approval
      ↓
Prod
```

Example:

```terraform
module "service_project" {
  source = "git::https://github.com/flowvelly/terraform-gke-service-project.git?ref=v1.2.0"
}
```

QA:

```text
v1.2.0
```

PreProd:

```text
v1.2.0
```

Prod:

```text
v1.2.0
```

No code drift between environments.

